OL,3,CEnergy price cap predicted to rise in
OL,4,CJanuary, raising household bills by 1%
OL,6,FThe energy price cap was introduced in
OL,7,FJanuary 2019 and sets a maximum price
OL,8,Fthat energy suppliers can charge
OL,9,Fconsumers in England, Scotland and
OL,10,FWales for each kilowatt hour of energy
OL,11,Fthey use.
OL,13,FIt does not limit total bills, because
OL,14,Fhouseholders still pay for the amount
OL,15,Fof energy they consume.
