OL,3,CEnergy price cap predicted to rise in
OL,4,CJanuary, raising household bills by 1%
OL,6,FMeanwhile, millions of pensioners are
OL,7,Ffacing a winter with less support,
OL,8,Fafter the new Government decided to
OL,9,Fscrap winter fuel payments for those
OL,10,Fwho do not receive pension credits or
OL,11,Fother benefits. About 10 million
OL,12,Fpensioners will miss out on the
OL,13,Fpayments of up to #300 this year.
OL,15,FThe energy price cap is still
OL,16,Fsignificantly lower than when the
OL,17,Fenergy crisis peaked following
OL,18,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine in 2022.
